---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="关于张涵 — 景观施工图设计师"
  description="张涵，景观施工图设计师，2017年入行，专注将景观方案转化为清晰、实用、可施工的图纸，服务西南地区住宅、社区、酒店及滨水景观项目。"
>
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-hero__inner">
        <div class="about-hero__text">
          <p class="label label-accent reveal">设计师简介</p>
          <h1 class="about-hero__name reveal reveal-delay-1">
            张涵
            <span class="about-hero__name-en h-en">Han Zhang</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="about-hero__role reveal reveal-delay-2">景观施工图设计师</p>
          <p class="about-hero__since reveal reveal-delay-3">入行 2017 · 9 年专注施工图</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-hero__photo reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="about-hero__photo-wrap">
            <img
              src="https://picsum.photos/seed/designer-portrait/600/750"
              alt="张涵设计师"
              width="600"
              height="750"
              loading="eager"
              fetchpriority="high"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="about-hero__photo-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-bio">
    <div class="container about-bio__inner">
      <div class="about-bio__main">
        <div class="about-bio__block reveal">
          <h2 class="h-lg">从业历程</h2>
          <div class="about-bio__text">
            <p>2017年，张涵正式踏入景观行业，从施工现场跟图起步，在实践中深刻理解了图纸语言与建造现实之间的落差——也由此找到了自己的专业方向：做连接设计与施工的那座桥梁。</p>
            <p>近十年间，张涵深耕施工图设计领域，服务四川成都、泸州、乐山及新疆和田等地的开发商与景观设计院，参与或主导了住宅景观、社区公园、酒店庭院、示范区样板间及滨水廊道等多类型项目的施工图工作。</p>
            <p>张涵的核心价值在于：将方案设计师的创意意图，转化为施工班组能够读懂、材料商能够报价、监理能够核验的规范图纸——让设计真正落地，而不仅停留在效果图上。</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-bio__block reveal">
          <h2 class="h-lg">专业价值观</h2>
          <div class="about-bio__text">
            <p>张涵相信，一套好的施工图不只是图纸的集合，而是对设计意图的忠实翻译、对施工逻辑的清晰梳理、对成本控制的主动介入。在设计细节的取舍之间，始终以"可落地、可控制、可维护"为判断标准。</p>
            <p>在气候适应性方面，张涵尤其关注西南地区高湿多雨的气候特征，以及新疆等极端干旱地区的特殊施工条件，擅长因地制宜地选择材料与节点构造，在保证耐久性的同时合理控制造价。</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-bio__block reveal">
          <h2 class="h-lg">专业技能</h2>
          <ul class="about-bio__credentials">
            <li>景观施工图深化设计（平面、竖向、铺装、种植、水电）</li>
            <li>施工节点大样绘制与构造详图</li>
            <li>材料选型与成本优化建议</li>
            <li>现场技术配合与图纸答疑</li>
            <li>设计变更说明与签证协助</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="about-bio__block reveal">
          <h2 class="h-lg">软件能力</h2>
          <div class="software-grid">
            <div class="software-item">
              <span class="software-item__name">AutoCAD</span>
              <span class="software-item__level">熟练</span>
            </div>
            <div class="software-item">
              <span class="software-item__name">Adobe Photoshop</span>
              <span class="software-item__level">熟练</span>
            </div>
            <div class="software-item">
              <span class="software-item__name">SketchUp</span>
              <span class="software-item__level">熟练</span>
            </div>
            <div class="software-item">
              <span class="software-item__name">Microsoft Office</span>
              <span class="software-item__level">熟练</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="about-bio__sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-card reveal">
          <h3 class="label label-accent">擅长项目类型</h3>
          <ul class="sidebar-card__list">
            <li>住宅景观施工图</li>
            <li>社区公园景观</li>
            <li>酒店庭院景观</li>
            <li>示范区样板间景观</li>
            <li>滨水景观廊道</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <h3 class="label label-accent">服务地区</h3>
          <ul class="sidebar-card__list">
            <li>四川成都（主要）</li>
            <li>四川泸州、乐山</li>
            <li>新疆和田</li>
            <li>西南地区（可远程配合）</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <h3 class="label label-accent">联系方式</h3>
          <div class="sidebar-card__contact">
            <a href="mailto:hello@zhanghandesign.com" class="contact-item">
              <span class="label">邮件</span>
              <span>hello@zhanghandesign.com</span>
            </a>
            <div class="contact-item">
              <span class="label">微信 / 电话</span>
              <span>请通过邮件联系后获取</span>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-item">
              <span class="label">工作方式</span>
              <span>驻场 / 远程配合均可</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-timeline">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="label label-accent reveal" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-12)">从业历程</p>
      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline__item reveal">
          <div class="timeline__year">2017</div>
          <div class="timeline__content">
            <h3 class="timeline__title">入行景观行业</h3>
            <p class="timeline__desc">正式踏入景观行业，从施工现场跟图与驻场配合起步，深度理解方案图纸与实际建造之间的落差，逐渐确立以施工图为核心的专业方向。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline__item reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="timeline__year">2019</div>
          <div class="timeline__content">
            <h3 class="timeline__title">独立承接施工图项目</h3>
            <p class="timeline__desc">开始独立承接景观施工图深化工作，服务成都本地开发商与设计院，首个代表项目为新疆和田滨江府高端住宅景观。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline__item reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="timeline__year">2020</div>
          <div class="timeline__content">
            <h3 class="timeline__title">拓展多类型项目</h3>
            <p class="timeline__desc">业务拓展至社区公园、酒店庭院等多种景观类型，同年完成成都川意中央公园及天府农博园酒店两个代表项目。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline__item reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <div class="timeline__year">2021</div>
          <div class="timeline__content">
            <h3 class="timeline__title">深耕示范区与住宅</h3>
            <p class="timeline__desc">服务泸州优品道示范区及乐山远山住宅项目，积累了示范区快速出图、山地竖向控制等专项经验。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline__item reveal">
          <div class="timeline__year">2023</div>
          <div class="timeline__content">
            <h3 class="timeline__title">承接滨水景观项目</h3>
            <p class="timeline__desc">完成成都金融滨湖湾滨水景观施工图，积累防腐木平台、生态护岸等滨水专项节点经验，持续服务西南地区优质项目。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
.about-hero { padding-top: clamp(6rem, 10vw, 12rem); padding-bottom: var(--space-section); background: var(--color-bg); overflow: hidden; }
.about-hero__inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 8rem); align-items: end; }
.about-hero__text { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-4); }
.about-hero__name { font-family: var(--font-serif-cn); font-size: var(--text-2xl); font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.1em; line-height: 1.0; color: var(--color-ink); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-3); }
.about-hero__name-en { font-size: 0.45em; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--color-ink-faint); }
.about-hero__role { font-family: var(--font-serif-cn); font-size: var(--text-md); font-weight: 300; color: var(--color-ink-muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
.about-hero__since { font-family: var(--font-serif-en); font-style: italic; font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-ink-faint); letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
.about-hero__photo { position: relative; }
.about-hero__photo-wrap { position: relative; z-index: 1; border-radius: var(--radius-md); overflow: hidden; aspect-ratio: 4/5; }
.about-hero__photo-wrap img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: top; filter: grayscale(15%); }
.about-hero__photo-bg { position: absolute; bottom: -1.5rem; right: -1.5rem; width: 70%; height: 70%; background: var(--color-accent-light); border-radius: var(--radius-md); z-index: 0; }
.about-bio { padding-block: var(--space-section); background: var(--color-bg-alt); }
.about-bio__inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr; gap: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 8rem); align-items: start; }
.about-bio__main { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-12); }
.about-bio__block { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-6); }
.about-bio__text { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-4); font-size: var(--text-sm); line-height: 1.9; color: var(--color-ink-muted); }
.about-bio__credentials { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-3); }
.about-bio__credentials li { font-family: var(--font-serif-cn); font-size: var(--text-base); font-weight: 300; color: var(--color-ink-muted); padding-left: var(--space-6); position: relative; }
.about-bio__credentials li::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); width: 6px; height: 1px; background: var(--color-accent); }
.software-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--space-3); }
.software-item { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4); background: var(--color-bg); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); border: 1px solid oklch(14% 0.01 60 / 0.07); }
.software-item__name { font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-ink); }
.software-item__level { font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-accent); letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
.about-bio__sidebar { position: sticky; top: 100px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-6); }
.sidebar-card { background: var(--color-surface); border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: var(--space-8); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-6); border: 1px solid oklch(14% 0.01 60 / 0.07); }
.sidebar-card__list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-3); }
.sidebar-card__list li { font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-ink-muted); padding-left: var(--space-4); position: relative; }
.sidebar-card__list li::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0.6em; width: 4px; height: 4px; background: var(--color-accent); border-radius: 50%; }
.sidebar-card__contact { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-4); }
.contact-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-1); font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-ink-muted); transition: color var(--duration-fast); }
a.contact-item:hover { color: var(--color-accent); }
.about-timeline { padding-block: var(--space-section); background: var(--color-bg); }
.timeline { display: flex; flex-direction: column; position: relative; padding-left: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 6rem); }
.timeline::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 3rem); top: 0.75em; bottom: 0; width: 1px; background: oklch(14% 0.01 60 / 0.12); }
.timeline__item { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr; gap: var(--space-8); padding-bottom: var(--space-12); position: relative; }
.timeline__item::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: calc(-1 * clamp(3rem, 6vw, 6rem) + clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 3rem) - 4px); top: 0.7em; width: 9px; height: 9px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--color-accent); border: 2px solid var(--color-bg); outline: 1px solid var(--color-accent); }
.timeline__year { font-family: var(--font-serif-en); font-style: italic; font-size: var(--text-md); font-weight: 300; color: var(--color-accent); padding-top: 0.1em; }
.timeline__content { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-3); }
.timeline__title { font-family: var(--font-serif-cn); font-size: var(--text-base); font-weight: 400; color: var(--color-ink); letter-spacing: 0.03em; }
.timeline__desc { font-size: var(--text-sm); line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-ink-muted); }
@media (max-width: 900px) { .about-hero__inner, .about-bio__inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .about-hero__photo { order: -1; max-width: 400px; margin: 0 auto; } .about-bio__sidebar { position: static; } }
@media (max-width: 640px) { .timeline { padding-left: 2.5rem; } .timeline__item { grid-template-columns: 60px 1fr; gap: var(--space-4); } .software-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
